videos.headline: Old Dominion's Harper with 97 yard kickoff TD
videos.description: Monarchs' Isaiah Harper returns the kickoff 97 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Johnson punches it in for a North Texas TD
videos.description: Evan Johnson rushes 6 yards for a touchdown to extend  the Mean Green lead to 21-10.

videos.headline: Wilson puts North Texas on the board first
videos.description: North Texas' Jeffery Wilson gets the hand off and runs the ball up the middle for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Harper returns his 2nd kickoff for TD
videos.description: Isaiah Harper takes the kickoff and runs it back 98 yards to the house for an Old Dominion touchdown. It's Harper's second kickoff touchdown return of the game.

videos.headline: Williams' TD puts Old Dominion in the lead
videos.description: Steven Williams' 10-yard touchdown run puts Old Dominion ahead for the first time in the game.

videos.headline: Mean Green retake lead on rushing TD
videos.description: Nic Smith rushes 20 yards to the end zone to put North Texas ahead in the fourth quarter.
